<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="arial">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>We have been attempting to contact you in relation to an outstanding balance for your insurance policy. As we haven’t been able to get in touch, </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">the outstanding balance is due to be referred to debt collection</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><b>It’s not too late to bring your payments up to date and prevent any further action</b></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">. Please call us on </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">01242 808740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> as soon as possible to discuss your options.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Regrettably, </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">if we do not hear from you in the next 7 days, the outstanding balance will be referred to a debt collection agency</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">, who will be in touch with you directly to explain the next steps.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Customer Accounts Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>